Packages 
Package Description
Catalano.Core
The Catalano.Core contains common classes used by other namespaces of the framework and classes, which can be used independently for various purposes.
Catalano.Core.Concurrent
The Catalano.Core.Concurrent contains parallel base classes used by other namespaces of the framework and classes, which can be used independently for various purposes.
Catalano.Core.Structs
The Catalano.Core.Structs contains common structured classes used by other namespaces of the framework and classes, which can be used independently for various purposes.
Catalano.Fuzzy
The Catalano.Fuzzy namespace contains set of interfaces and classes to operate with fuzzy sets.
Catalano.Graph
The Catalano.Graph namespace contains the base of the graph.
Catalano.Graph.Network
The Catalano.Graph.Network namespace contains algorithms of network in the graph.
Catalano.Graph.Pathfinding
The Catalano.Graph.Pathfinding contains common interfaces to specified algorithms in pathfinding.
Catalano.Graph.Pathfinding.AStar
The Catalano.Graph.Pathfinding.AStar contains AStar (A*) algorithm and classes used.
Catalano.Imaging
The Catalano.Imaging contains base class for manipulation of pixels.
Catalano.Imaging.ActiveContour.Ovuscule  
Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent
The Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent namespace contains base classes for share data among the theads.
Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent.Filters
The Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent.Filters namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image processing filters running in parallel.
Catalano.Imaging.Corners
The Catalano.Imaging.Corners contains Interest point detectors (i.e Harris, Susan and FREAK).
Catalano.Imaging.Corners.FREAK
The Catalano.Imaging.Corners.FREAK contains classes used in Fast Retina Keypoint (FREAK).
Catalano.Imaging.Filters
The Catalano.Imaging.Filters namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image processing filters.
Catalano.Imaging.Filters.Artistic
The Catalano.Imaging.Filters.Artistic namespace contains collection classes, which provide different artistic filters.
Catalano.Imaging.Shapes
The Catalano.Imaging.Shapes namespace contains collection classes, which provide shapes.
Catalano.Imaging.Tools
The Catalano.Imaging.Tools namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image moments, analysis textures.
Catalano.IO
The Catalano.IO contains tools for read and write files like CSV.
Catalano.MachineLearning
The Catalano.MachineLearning namespace contains interfaces and classes for different algorithms of machine learning.
Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification
The Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification namespace contains interfaces and classes for classifications.
Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification.DecisionTrees
The Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification.DecisionTrees namespace contains decision trees algorithms.
Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification.DecisionTrees.Learning
The Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification.DecisionTrees.Learning namespace contains decision trees learning algorithms.
Catalano.MachineLearning.Exploration
The Catalano.MachineLearning.Exploration namespace contains interfaces and classes for exploration algorithms of machine learning.
Catalano.MachineLearning.Performance
The Catalano.MachineLearning.Performance namespace contains interfaces and classes for performance measure classification.
Catalano.MachineLearning.Regression
The Catalano.MachineLearning.Regression namespace contains classes for different algorithms for regressions.
Catalano.MachineLearning.Regression.RegressionTrees
The Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification.RegressionTrees namespace contains regression trees algorithms.
Catalano.MachineLearning.Regression.RegressionTrees.Learning
The Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification.RegressionTrees.Learning namespace contains regression trees learning algorithms.
Catalano.Math
The Catalano.Math namespace contains set of math utilities, which are used by other Catalano framework's namespaces or may be used individually.
Catalano.Math.Decompositions
The Catalano.Math.Decompositions namespace contains set of math decompositions (SVD, QR, LU, ...) which are used by other Catalano framework's namespaces or may be used individually.
Catalano.Math.Dissimilarities  
Catalano.Math.Distances
The Catalano.Math.Distances namespace contains set of distances (Euclidean, Manhattan, Chessboard, ...) which are used by other Catalano framework's namespaces or may be used individually.
Catalano.Math.Functions
The Catalano.Math.Functions namespace contains set of functions as Normal, Gamma and others.
Catalano.Math.Geometry
The Catalano.Math.Geometry namespace contains set of geometry utilities, which are used by other Catalano namespaces or may be used individually.
Catalano.Math.Transforms
The Catalano.Math.Transforms namespace contains set of transforms.
Catalano.Math.Wavelets
The Catalano.Math.Wavelets namespace contains Wavelets transform such as the Haar Wavelet transforms.
Catalano.Neuro
The Catalano.Neuro namespace contains interfaces and classes for neural networks computations.
Catalano.Neuro.Learning
The Catalano.Neuro.Learning namespace contains interfaces and classes for neurons and neural networks learning.
Catalano.Signal  
Catalano.Statistics
The Catalano.Statistics namespace contains set of statistics utilities, which are used by other Catalano framework's namespaces or may be used individually.
Catalano.Statistics.Distributions
The Catalano.Statistics.Distribution namespace contains statistical distributions.
Catalano.Statistics.Kernels
The Catalano.Statistics.Kernels namespace contains kernel functions for machine learning and statistical applications.
Catalano.Statistics.Regression
The Catalano.Statistics.Regression namespace contains regression functions statistical applications.
Catalano.Vision
The Catalano.Vision contains filters used for sequence of images.
Catalano.Vision.Detection  
Catalano.Vision.SpatioTemporal
The Catalano.Vision.SpatioTemporal contains filters in spatio temporal for image processing.
Catalano.Vision.Temporal
The Catalano.Vision.Temporal contains temporal filters for image processing.
Catalano.Vision.Tools
